<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/improvisation/play-multiple-octave-scales-like-bad-ass.html">How to play multiple octave scales &#8211; like a bad-ass! (L#147)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
